{"tid":2275422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泛民被指違特權法 胡志偉斥 控方警察沆瀣一氣","createTime":"2020-11-07T06:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:28:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37691d93dbd90542833656ec3f33b60474d6e6bb","tid":2275422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/PM7QWL4ZHBBIHJQQWTFBVXIMLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FPM7QWL4ZHBBIHJQQWTFBVXIMLU%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=6e83d720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FPM7QWL4ZHBBIHJQQWTFBVXIMLU%2F&h=ec0035fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/PM7QWL4ZHBBIHJQQWTFBVXIMLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泛民被指違特權法 胡志偉斥 控方警察沆瀣一氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BGMcFGktY9lmxDCsa46ExjKjudc=/1162x810/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VCNYOEBJSFATRMAWNG36TJXJXA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBGMcFGktY9lmxDCsa46ExjKjudc%3D%2F1162x810%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVCNYOEBJSFATRMAWNG36TJXJXA.gif&h=9f902d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多名民主派被告昨到庭，聲援者高舉「政治打壓可恥」標語抗議檢控。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政權封殺議會抗爭，律政司日前引用《立法會（權力及特權）條例》，起訴八名時任立法會議員及議助，指他們今年5月8日阻礙選舉內務委員會主席及抗拒保安。案件昨日提堂，並押後至明年2月11日再訊，其間各人獲准保釋。身為被告的民主黨主席胡志偉庭外批評，政府、律政司與警方沆瀣一氣，針對性地檢控反對聲音，製造白色恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n容海恩陸頌雄列控方證人<br />\n<br />\n八名被告分別為民主黨立法會議員許智峯（38歲）、尹兆堅（51歲）、黃碧雲（61歲）、胡志偉（58歲）、工黨立法會議員張超雄（63歲）、工黨主席郭永健（33歲），以及前議員陳志全（48歲）和朱凱廸（43歲）。據悉，新民黨容海恩及工聯會陸頌雄被列為控方證人。<br />\n<br />\n除了胡外的其餘七人均被控一項藐視罪，指他們在委員會會議上引起騷亂，令會議程序中斷或相當可能中斷。許、。。。。。。。。。。。。，該案爭議點包括特權法可否用於控告議員。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸庭外表示，預計涉及議會的檢控「陸續有嚟」，直言「共產黨用呢啲旁門左道方法，將不同罪名冧喺我哋身上；但放馬過嚟啦，你冧得幾多，我都承受得起，香港人係唔會放棄」。陳志全指控方要求他們保釋期間居於報稱地址，相信是為方便警方上門拘捕。張超雄則強調，政治爭議應在議會內解決，但政權無所不用其極，「執法完全偏袒，條紅線越畫越埋」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3842/20"},{"pid":"ea2537795d4feb31e92f5ee51351ad359b5cc6cf","tid":2275422,"uid":195211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"講到好似今日先知 一早退出咗咪得囉<br />\n講廢話"},{"pid":"3f47108621b8a9bfea8b39600b70b6035043dd7a","tid":2275422,"uid":147182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"拉晒佢地就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月袋10皮咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707c35fb074e7cbd9f95fa94656c978cab35c8ce","tid":2275422,"uid":39653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}